snippet.textDisplay:
Coke studio , please keep the level of professionalism and music bar high. Your level is javed bashir, Akbar Ali, rahat father Ali khan, Amjad sabri and other great singers. I am in no way against new singers but please give chance to people who knows the music and are good at it . It's ok to bring a new face once in a while but please stay away from all these shifarasi. Look at these two, I am very disappointed. Ali zafar himself don't know what the hell to do, he's an actor , he's trying to be a singer and lastly a joker. Now he has introduced his brother who needs lots of musical help. In the mean time you could have given a chance to much deserving singer.Quality music and rohail hayat music is not about open shirt or shirtless , long hair , and making weird sounds. Please say no to all these people and let them know if they want to sing at coke studio then they need to start taking classes with javeed bashir or other quality singers. 
Make yourself that kind of singer where  coke studio will be honored to sing for them.
